Title: S6 Ep. 270 Victoria Yampolsky - Voted #1 Fan Fav from 2022 Guest
Description:
S6 Ep. 270 Victoria Yampolsky   Having Victoria Yampolsky as a guest on my show was incredibly thought provoking and encouraging. She is an expert on financial strategy, female entrepreneurship funding, and AI. 

We hope you enjoy this show and listen all the way to the end to hear her mentoring advice that benefits all listeners regardless of who you are. Here is a bite of what you can hear when you listen to the podcast. We all have dreams and they may seem unattainable. There is more to that quote.
